vulnerability.name: USN-6191-1
vulnerability.description: USN-6081-1, USN-6084-1, USN-6092-1 and USN-6095-1 fixed vulnerabilities in the Linux kernel. Unfortunately, that update introduced a spurious warning in the IPv6 subsystem. This update removes the undesired warning message.

statements.status_notes: The system could show undesired warning messages in certain conditions.
